ed="T" n="0843b05"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0843b05"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000005362"><placeName>五臺山</placeName><placeName>華嚴寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A012781">牛雲</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0843b06"/><persName key="A012781">釋牛雲</persName>，俗姓<name>趙</name>，<placeName key="PL000000005470">雁門</placeName>人也。童蒙之歲有似<lb
ed="T" n="0843b07"/>神不足，遣入鄉校，終日不知一字。惟見<lb
ed="T" n="0843b08"/>僧尼，合掌有畏憚之貌。<date key="j19709111971293" from-iso="+0684-01-26" to-iso="+0685-02-11">年甫十二</date>，二親送<lb
ed="T" n="0843b09"/>往<placeName key="PL000000005392"><placeName>五臺</placeName><placeName>華嚴寺</placeName><placeName>善住閣院</placeName></placeName>出家，<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz11"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz11"/><persName key="A012785">淨覺</persName><ptr target="#n2685"/>為<lb
ed="T" n="0843b10"/>師。每令負薪汲水，時眾輕其朴鈍，多以<lb
ed="T" n="0843b11"/>謔浪歸之。年滿受具，益難誦習。及年<date key="j19796821980065" from-iso="+0708-02-01" to-iso="+0709-02-18">三十<lb
ed="T" n="0843b12"/>有六</date><ptr target="#n2686"/>，乃言曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012781">我</ref>聞臺上恒有<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>現形。<ref type="person" target="#A012781">我</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0843b13"/>今跣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1661"/>足而去，儻見<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>，惟求聰明，學誦經<lb
ed="T" n="0843b14"/>法耳。」時冒寒雪，情無退屈，至<placeName key="PL000000005345">東臺</placeName>頂，見<lb
ed="T" n="0843b15"/>一老人然火而坐。<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>問曰：「如此雪寒，從何<lb
ed="T" n="0843b16"/>而來？」老人曰：「吾從<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>川</sic><corr>山</corr></choice>下<ptr target="#n2687"/>來」<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>曰：「從何道上，<lb
ed="T" n="0843b17"/>何無屨跡？」曰：「吾雪前來。」老人却問<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>曰：「有<lb
ed="T" n="0843b18"/>何心願，犯雪徒跣而至，豈不苦也？」<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012781">吾</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0843b19"/>雖為僧，自恨昏鈍，不能誦念經法。此來欲<lb
ed="T" n="0843b20"/>求見<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>，只乞聰明果報。」老人曰：「奇哉！」又<lb
ed="T" n="0843b21"/>曰：「此處不見<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>，更欲何之？」<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>曰：「欲上<lb
ed="T" n="0843b22"/><placeName key="PL000000005324">北臺</placeName>去。」老人曰：「吾意亦然。」曰：「請<ref type="person" target="#A012781">師</ref>先行。」<ptr target="#n615"/><persName key="A012781">雲</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0843b23"/>乃遊遍臺頂，告別老人，自西而去。薄暮，方<lb
ed="T" n="0843b24"/>到<placeName key="PL000000005324">北臺</placeName>，又見老人然火而坐，頗為驚怪。問<lb
ed="T" n="0843b25"/>曰：「適於<placeName key="PL000000005345">東臺</placeName>相別，為何先至？」老人曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012781">師</ref>不<lb
ed="T" n="0843b26"/>知要路，所以來遲。」<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>雖承此語，心乃猶豫，<lb
ed="T" n="0843b27"/>只此老人莫應<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>也？<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>乃<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz13"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>鳴</sic><corr>嗚</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz13"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g385"/>足<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz15"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz15"/>拜。老<lb
ed="T" n="0843b28"/>人曰：「吾俗人也，不應作<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz17"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz17"/>。」唯貪設<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz19"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz19"/>，情屬<lb
ed="T" n="0843b29"/>不移<ptr target="#n616"/>。良久，老人云：「休<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz21"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz21"/>，候吾入定，觀<ref type="person" target="#A012781">汝</ref>前<pb ed="T" n="0843c" xml:id="T50.2061.0843c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0843c01"/>身作何行業而昏鈍也。」老人閉目，倏爾開<lb
ed="T" n="0843c02"/>顏語<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012781">汝</ref>前生為牛來，因載藏經，今得<lb
ed="T" n="0843c03"/>為僧而闇鈍耳<ptr target="#n2688"/>。<ref type="person" target="#A012781">汝</ref>於<placeName key="PL000000059375">龍堂</placeName>邊取一<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz23"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic><g ref="#Z1251"/></sic><corr>钁</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz23"/>來，<lb
ed="T" n="0843c04"/>與<ref type="person" target="#A012781">汝</ref>斸却心頭淤肉，即明快<ptr target="#n2689"/>也。」<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>遂得<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz24"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic><g ref="#Z1251"/></sic><corr>钁</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz24"/><lb
ed="T" n="0843c05"/>度與。老人曰：「<persName key="A012781">汝</persName>但閉目，候吾教開即開。」因<lb
ed="T" n="0843c06"/>閉目，次有似當心施<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz25"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic><g ref="#Z1251"/></sic><corr>钁</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz25"/>，身無痛苦，心乃豁<lb
ed="T" n="0843c07"/>然，似闇室立於明燈，巨夜懸於圓月也。<lb
ed="T" n="0843c08"/><persName key="A012781">雲</persName>開目乃見老人現<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>像，語<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012781">汝</ref>自<lb
ed="T" n="0843c09"/>後誦念經法，歷耳無忘。又於<placeName key="PL000000005363"><placeName>華嚴寺</placeName><placeName>㵎東<lb
ed="T" n="0843c10"/>院</placeName></placeName>大有因緣，無得退轉。」<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>乃行悲行泣，接<lb
ed="T" n="0843c11"/>足而<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz26"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz26"/>，未舉頭<anchor xml:id="beg0843001"/>頃<anchor xml:id="end0843001"/>，不見<ref type="person" target="#A002144">菩薩</ref>矣。<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>後下<lb
ed="T" n="0843c12"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000005250">山</ref>，四支無損<ptr target="#n2690"/>，凡曰經典，目所一覽，輒誦於<lb
ed="T" n="0843c13"/>口。<date from-iso="+0709-06-16" key="j19801831980212" to-iso="+0709-07-15">明年夏五月</date>，遶<placeName key="PL000000005450">育王塔</placeName>行道念經。至更<lb
ed="T" n="0843c14"/>初，乃見一道直光<ptr target="#n617"/>從<placeName key="PL000000005324">北臺</placeName>頂連瑞塔基<ptr target="#n2691"/>，久<lb
ed="T" n="0843c15"/>而不散，於光明中現寶閣一所，前有金牌，<lb
ed="T" n="0843c16"/>題云「善住」。<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>憶<persName key="A002144">菩薩</persName>授記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1351"/>之言，依光中所現<lb
ed="T" n="0843c17"/>之閣而建置焉。道化施行，人咸貴重。於<date from-iso="+0735-02-02" key="j19895451989927" to-iso="+0736-02-19"><name>開元</name><lb
ed="T" n="0843c18"/>二十三年</date>無疾而終，俗齡六十三，法臘四十<lb
ed="T" n="0843c19"/>四矣。<persName key="A012781">雲</persName>名亡上字，承<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>記識本迹為牛，<lb
ed="T" n="0843c20"/>故時號之焉。</p>
